{"tid":1822770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我有時夠幫親藍店，就算比人影我又唔會少條毛","createTime":"2020-01-13T07:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T12:36:59.000Z","uid":88737,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"03421ba17d683c7334fdcc4da7a1d59d328b5e90","tid":1822770,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T07:06:13.000Z","msg":"平時我都會盡量食黃，有時可能無得選擇食藍，就算我比人影放上網我唔覺得有乜大不了，有無用先唔講<br />\n對比起好多手足受既苦作出既犧牲，請問你會少左條毛？<br />\n<br />\n見到個post話咁樣係極權，（先唔講對付極權真係要用番佢既手段）<br />\n<br />\n睇黎好多人對同路人既道德標準仲高過對中共，咁樣就已經係極權咁呢世都唔洗贏到中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n半年啦，肯用下個腦未？唔好再比5毛帶風向啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0db744889e30f7b91a2a50dec07add22c01fe1","tid":1822770,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T07:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rU0YvgW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrU0YvgW.gif&h=a8a4f0d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3455a8a83304728909a925283481a532303c7485","tid":1822770,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T07:24:05.000Z","msg":"無人推"},{"pid":"61f2e224b4ad09e3182418a16fc9cb748f898082","tid":1822770,"uid":325098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T07:27:04.000Z","msg":"要完全唔幫襯藍店好難<br />\n但要減少幫襯就好易<br />\n慢慢減少就得<br />\n唔駛急<br />\n要漫長的戰爭<br />\n大家努力"},{"pid":"0e8694c10f6d455842d6a2f0a5d97e129bc4ebb2","tid":1822770,"uid":73004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T07:41:14.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n<br />\n手足要影唔會怪你地，不割<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2555f192dbad783349b127d4dfd22c8467dbf0d","tid":1822770,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T12:36:59.000Z","msg":"仲係度拗緊，但無人理我"}]}